history.content:
<md>Hey all,

Every year, the EECS department designs an official undergraduate experience survey sent out to all undergraduate students affiliated with the department, asking questions about topics ranging from class experiences to mental health issues to budget concerns. In the Spring, the results of the survey are aggregated and presented to all EECS faculty. 
  
This year, we have room for some extra questions; we're taking suggestions for questions that can address issues that are currently lacking in the survey, and would love to hear from you!  
  
_Please submit any survey suggestions to the form linked below_. The form will close on **Monday, December 6th** at 11:59 PM. 

[https://hkn.mu/eecs-ugrad-survey-question-submission](https://hkn.mu/eecs-ugrad-survey-question-submission)

Please feel free to email deprel@hkn.mu with any questions! Thanks for your time!</md>
